lmate<br />\n分手其實對雙方都係解脫，頹個位係我作為男朋友真係做得唔稱職，即使成個旅程完左，佢都隨時唔開心同辛苦多過幸福"},{"pid":"ab8160a507d25d02dd07736cb6684fc125c1f73d","tid":972981,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"最後訓得三個鐘就返工<br />\n極之唔夠精神<br />\n但一到日光時段個人都無咁鬱悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e091e6a7fd1b5b77e23255f5f50b3a06bea91a70","tid":972981,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71eeb2091801dc9f98960ddf54360c6e63c77635","tid":972981,"uid":162112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T20:02:19.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣ching<br />\n一齊三年 一個幾月前被分手 真係愈嚟愈頹 日日天光先攰到訓著 然後發夢又同佢復合 醒翻知道係夢真係好痛好辛苦<br />\n加油呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"被又好 自己提出又好 分得手都好應該睇清係咪有咩零件未上齊 定係本身就唔啱大細<br />\n我而家係後者 所以想復合既心當然有 但大個仔無可能話想就想既"},{"pid":"fb1ae7ddff2b397d7f3df7151051c97c82e392ac","tid":972981,"uid":84363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:30:49.000Z","msg":"係 好後悔當初對佢唔夠好"},{"pid":"d92e05f8bd6c540c70c3d64dd7df3ed3a16cb155","tid":972981,"uid":138748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:33:27.000Z","msg":"最大的傷害唔係來自分手，係來自後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4387e80cb156028b45825e565cd233d64875481","tid":972981,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"三個月啦 都仲好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883f59f5ad1996c606cfcbda07ec26b2a50eb8bb","tid":972981,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92e05f8bd6c540c70c3d64dd7df3ed3a16cb155","tid":972981,"uid":138748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:33:27.000Z","msg":"最大的傷害唔係來自分手，係來自後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"其實好多野都係雙方 所以好討厭人分對錯<br />\n但後悔既係自己應該盡力做好既地方反而忽略<br />\n識得後悔同反省我覺得係呢段感情教育我既<br />\n以前自己真係好自我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5001adc3c91eb7f2baeed0185c2b5f0d0e5e774","tid":972981,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4387e80cb156028b45825e565cd233d64875481","tid":972981,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"三個月啦 都仲好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"辛苦喺邊先"},{"pid":"1066b818237e1ee947e7a6abb951cf26301d968a","tid":972981,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"樓主我8年，聖誕佢同我分手又係block我wtsapp,我仲戴撚埋帽呀，頭果幾日我都好唔撚開心呀，點解要咁撚樣呃9我，打黎喊晒口同我講對唔住，依家我就睇撚化左左，我做好自己，就睇呢啲人幾耐會散"},{"pid":"b98a5b9a3d846b9dde5065c6cd3c60c14b7b895b","tid":972981,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5001adc3c91eb7f2baeed0185c2b5f0d0e5e774","tid":972981,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4387e80cb156028b45825e565cd233d64875481","tid":972981,"uid":217146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"三個月啦 都仲好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"辛苦喺邊先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"成個人無哂動力 集中唔到<br />\n做返或者行返同佢行過既路 d回憶會湧上黎<br />\n佢一有少少動作就會好影響心情 情緒大上大落<br />\n想收埋自己 好怕人多既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b645d591aa1283ce4cde01c26df1b3234474e43c","tid":972981,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nzik3trQPtE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fnzik3trQPtE&d=V7LlLSrrJUberb4%2Fsy9RMf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=61940ab6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nzik3trQPtE</a><br />\n奶共校長首幻影，而家聽好有感覺。<br />\n「紫色的小盒子裡<br />\n盡藏著許多未了事<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n睡夢裡<br />\n追憶裡<br />\n在尋覓你的影子」"}]}